data.description: ~TWO BRAND NEW HVAC SYSTEMS INSTALLED NOV 2023. NEW CARPET IN ALL BEDROOMS INSTALLED APRIL 2023. ONE WATER HEATER REPLACED SEPTEMBER 2022!~  LOCAL BANK OFFERING 0 DOWN, NO PMI & $7000 FOR CLOSING COST OR DPA WITH BUY DOWN AVAIL. ASK ME HOW!~  Welcome to Grove Park, a beautiful master-planned community that is minutes from all Montgomery has to offer! With over 3100 sqft, this 4 bedroom 4 bath home offers spacious rooms and walk-in closets in a gated community..The large windows throughout the home lets natural light into all rooms. The kitchen has a large island, touchless kitchen faucet, under cabinet lighting and an electric range but is also plumbed for gas. The sliding glass door in breakfast nook gives access to the cute grilling porch on side of house. Refrigerator in laundry and kitchen remain. Large en suite main bedroom has custom walk-in closet. Both downstairs bathrooms have comfort height toilets. The two huge bedrooms that flank the stairs are both en suite and each has a walk-in closet. If storage is what you need, this home has it. There is a storage closet in the laundry, a walk-in pantry under the stairs, a utility/storage room in the garage and 2 floored attic spaces. This neighborhood boasts quiet tree-lined streets, walking/biking trails, 2 fully-stocked lakes, fishing pier and arbor, a playground, resident-leased garden plots at The Farm, neighborhood pharmacy and a woodworking shop. Enjoy gatherings at the private clubhouse with attached fitness center with locker rooms, massage room & neighborhood library. Play in the enclosed heated saltwater community pool or wine down in the hot tub. Make reservations for clubhouse, pool, playground, golf cart and place work orders through the neighborhood concierge. Relax on the weekends due to the benefits of neighborhood lawn maintenance that covers mowing, edging, trimming, pine straw, chemical treatments and irrigation. Come see why Grove Park is truly "A Neighborhood for Living!"
